{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"HTMLDialogElement: cancel イベント","mdn_url":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/cancel_event","locale":"ja","native":"日本語","sidebarHTML":"<ol><li><strong><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement\"><code>HTMLDialogElement</code></a></strong></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>プロパティ</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/open\"><code>open</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/returnValue\"><code>returnValue</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>メソッド</summary><ol><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/close\"><code>close()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/show\"><code>show()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/showModal\"><code>showModal()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><em><code>cancel</code></em></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-experimental\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-experimental\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/close_event\"><code>close</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLElement\"><code>HTMLElement</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Element\"><code>Element</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Node\"><code>Node</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<div id=\"sect1\"></div>\n\n<p><strong><code>cancel</code></strong> イベントは、ユーザーが現在開いているダイアログを閉じたいと操作したときに <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dialog\"><code>&lt;dialog&gt;</code></a> に発生します。例えば、ユーザーがブラウザーの UI の中で <kbd>Esc</kbd> キーを押したり、「ダイアログを閉じる」ボタンをクリックしたりしたときにブラウザーがこのイベントを発生させることがあります。</p>\n\n<table class=\"properties\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">バブリング</th>\n   <td>なし</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">キャンセル</th>\n   <td>可</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">インターフェイス</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">イベントハンドラープロパティ</th>\n   <td><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/oncancel\" title=\"oncancel\"><code>oncancel</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"examples","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"live_example","title":"ライブ例","isH3":true,"content":"<h4 id=\"html\">HTML</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>dialog</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>example-dialog<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>close<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">type</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>reset<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Close<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>dialog</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>button</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>open-dialog<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>Open dialog<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>button</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>result<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span></code></pre></div>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"js\">JS</h4>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> result <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.result'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> dialog <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.example-dialog'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\ndialog<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'cancel'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'dialog was canceled'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> openDialog <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.open-dialog'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\nopenDialog<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token keyword\">if</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token keyword\">typeof</span> dialog<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>showModal <span class=\"token operator\">===</span> <span class=\"token string\">'function'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      dialog<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">showModal</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n      result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">''</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      result<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>textContent <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token string\">'The dialog API is not supported by this browser'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n\n<span class=\"token keyword\">const</span> closeButton <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> document<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">querySelector</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'.close'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\ncloseButton<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'click'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    dialog<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">close</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n\n<h4 id=\"result\" name=\"Result\">結果</h4>\n\n<p><iframe class=\"sample-code-frame\" title=\"Live example sample\" id=\"frame_live_example\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100px\" src=\"https://yari-demos.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/cancel_event/_sample_.live_example.html\" loading=\"lazy\"></iframe></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様書","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様書</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状態</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-cancel\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML Living Standard<br><small lang=\"ja\">cancel の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-living\">現行の標準</span></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility","isH3":false,"query":"api.HTMLDialogElement.cancel_event","dataURL":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/cancel_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"see_also","title":"関連情報","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/GlobalEventHandlers/oncancel\"><code>GlobalEventHandlers.oncancel</code></a></li>\n <li>HTML <a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/HTML/Element/dialog\"><code>&lt;dialog&gt;</code></a> element</li>\n <li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/close_event\" title=\"close\"><code>close</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"例","id":"examples"},{"text":"仕様書","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザーの互換性","id":"browser_compatibility"},{"text":"関連情報","id":"see_also"}],"summary":"cancel イベントは、ユーザーが現在開いているダイアログを閉じたいと操作したときに <dialog> に発生します。例えば、ユーザーがブラウザーの UI の中で Esc キーを押したり、「ダイアログを閉じる」ボタンをクリックしたりしたときにブラウザーがこのイベントを発生させることがあります。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLDialogElement: cancel event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"ja/web/api/htmldialogelement/cancel_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/web/api/htmldialogelement/cancel_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web","title":"開発者向けのウェブ技術"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement","title":"HTMLDialogElement"},{"uri":"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLDialogElement/cancel_event","title":"HTMLDialo